data.description: Quiet and Peaceful is the setting for this 3 BR 2BA home built in 2002, located near downtown Eustis, this home overlooks wooded area around Lake Dot. Kitchen has plenty of storage & counter space, plus brand new S.S. Refrigerator, Convection Stove & dishwasher. Home features a great room, an open floor plan with a spacious kitchen and dining area. Back yard is completely fenced.
